00:13:53,499 --> 00:13:55,918
Apa serunya jika kita tak makan
belut hari ini?

241
00:13:56,043 --> 00:13:58,838
Kalau begitu, boleh kita undang Kopral Do?

242
00:13:59,422 --> 00:14:02,591
Kopral Do sedikit…

243
00:14:02,758 --> 00:14:05,594
Kita telepon saja dia.
Dia bekerja dengan kita hari ini.

244
00:14:06,929 --> 00:14:07,930
Kita telepon?

245
00:14:08,389 --> 00:14:09,557
Haruskah kutelepon?

246
00:14:13,394 --> 00:14:14,854
Halo? Kopral Do?

247
00:14:15,271 --> 00:14:17,440
Kau ada rencana apa
sepulang kerja hari ini?

248
00:14:20,109 --> 00:14:22,570
Tak perlu menjelaskan detail. Tak apa.

249
00:14:22,653 --> 00:14:23,904
Dah.

250
00:14:24,655 --> 00:14:25,865
Jadi, apa dia datang?

251
00:14:26,282 --> 00:14:27,325
Dia ada kegiatan.

252
00:14:50,681 --> 00:14:52,600
Kau menginginkan cinta, bukan?

253
00:14:54,977 --> 00:14:56,270
Cinta apanya.

254
00:14:56,771 --> 00:14:59,565
Kau kecewa karena ibumu
tak cukup mencintaimu.

255
00:14:59,899 --> 00:15:00,941
Sialan.

256
00:15:01,025 --> 00:15:02,735
Kenapa kau bicara soal ibuku?

257
00:15:04,195 --> 00:15:05,404
Duduk tegak!

258
00:15:11,160 --> 00:15:13,454
Kecuali kau ingin pamanmu menusukmu.

259
00:15:23,089 --> 00:15:24,090
Kau…

260
00:15:25,508 --> 00:15:27,635
Kau ingin pengakuan dari pamanmu.

261
00:15:28,177 --> 00:15:29,553
Aku benar atau salah?

262
00:15:32,681 --> 00:15:33,724
Ya.

263
00:15:34,683 --> 00:15:36,018
Kau benar.

264
00:15:36,143 --> 00:15:37,520
Jangan cemas.

265
00:15:37,645 --> 00:15:39,563
Kecelakaan ini hanya permulaan bagimu.

266
00:15:39,814 --> 00:15:40,856
Apa?

267
00:15:41,357 --> 00:15:42,733
Itu berkat terselubung.

268
00:15:43,317 --> 00:15:46,904
Jika kau membereskannya dengan baik,
semua akan berjalan sesuai maumu.

269
00:15:48,823 --> 00:15:49,907
Sungguh?

270
00:15:51,992 --> 00:15:52,993
Tentu saja.

271
00:15:55,413 --> 00:15:56,455
Sungguh?

272
00:15:58,582 --> 00:15:59,917
Lalu aku harus apa?

273
00:16:03,129 --> 00:16:05,673
Hei, kau tak lapar? Aku kelaparan.

274
00:16:07,299 --> 00:16:09,427
-Letnan.
-Ya?

275
00:16:09,510 --> 00:16:11,804
Boleh aku tak ikut makan malam
dan pulang?

276
00:16:11,887 --> 00:16:13,264
Baiklah. Silakan.

277
00:16:13,347 --> 00:16:15,015
-Ya, Pak. Sungai Han.
-Sungai Han.

278
00:16:15,099 --> 00:16:17,435
-Sampai… Astaga!
-Aku tepat waktu, 'kan?

279
00:16:17,518 --> 00:16:18,519
Ya.

280
00:16:20,813 --> 00:16:23,816
-Katamu dia ada kegiatan.
-Ini kejutan.

281
00:16:23,899 --> 00:16:26,068
Hei, Aneh. Apa itu?

282
00:16:26,152 --> 00:16:28,195
Kuminta dia mampir mengambil daging.

283
00:16:28,279 --> 00:16:29,613
-Ini pasti berat.
-Tak apa.

284
00:16:29,738 --> 00:16:31,365
Bukannya kau bilang mau pulang?

285
00:16:31,991 --> 00:16:33,951
Mana bisa kubiarkan Kopral Do bawa ini?

286
00:16:34,034 --> 00:16:35,077
-Baiklah.
-Ya.

287
00:16:35,161 --> 00:16:36,287
Itu karung beras?

288
00:16:36,370 --> 00:16:37,496
Itu besar, 'kan?

289
00:16:39,331 --> 00:16:42,877
Aku tak tahu soal Sersan Han,
tapi aku tahu kau akan datang.

290
00:16:43,586 --> 00:16:44,628
Sungguh?

291
00:16:45,171 --> 00:16:46,464
Berapa lama kau bawa ini?

292
00:16:46,547 --> 00:16:48,048
-Ini sangat berat.
-Biar kubawa.

293
00:16:48,132 --> 00:16:49,508
-Tak berat bagiku.
-Tidak.

294
00:16:50,426 --> 00:16:52,344
Aku tak bisa biarkan wanita bawa ini.

295
00:16:56,432 --> 00:16:58,350
-Kopral Kim.
-Ya?

296
00:16:59,560 --> 00:17:02,104
Perlakukan aku sebagai rekan,
bukan wanita.

297
00:17:03,105 --> 00:17:04,356
Baiklah, tapi…

298
00:17:04,815 --> 00:17:06,150
Kau bukan pria.

299
00:17:06,734 --> 00:17:08,444
Kalau begitu, anggap aku pria.

300
00:17:12,948 --> 00:17:15,743
Sial, dia keren. Tunggu aku!

301
00:17:17,870 --> 00:17:19,288
Kau ini kenapa?

302
00:17:20,789 --> 00:17:23,792
-Kita mau ke mana?
-Kau harus coba restoran ini.

303
00:17:28,380 --> 00:17:30,174
Aku undang dia untuk makan malam.

304
00:17:30,299 --> 00:17:32,092
Kau yang membantu kami tadi.

305
00:17:33,719 --> 00:17:35,679
Hei, ayolah.

306
00:17:35,763 --> 00:17:37,932
-Ayo. Aku kelaparan.
-Ayo.

307
00:17:38,015 --> 00:17:39,850
Ayo, cepat. Aku lapar.

308
00:17:39,934 --> 00:17:41,602
-Berikan dagingnya.
-Tak apa.

309
00:17:41,685 --> 00:17:42,811
Akan kubawa.

310
00:17:52,863 --> 00:17:53,906
Ayo makan.

311
00:17:53,989 --> 00:17:55,741
-Terima kasih.
-Selamat makan.

312
00:17:57,117 --> 00:17:58,118
Kau menyelam scuba?

313
00:17:58,410 --> 00:17:59,537
Ya.

314
00:18:01,330 --> 00:18:02,498
Tapi itu merah muda…

315
00:18:02,915 --> 00:18:06,168
-Itu miliknya.
-Pria sejati pakai merah muda.

316
00:18:08,379 --> 00:18:12,216
Itu benar. Pria sejati suka merah muda.

317
00:18:12,299 --> 00:18:13,592
Aku tak suka merah muda.

318
00:18:13,676 --> 00:18:15,219
Kau suka merah muda.

319
00:18:15,719 --> 00:18:17,179
Kau lihat ini merah muda?

320
00:18:17,304 --> 00:18:19,640
-Dagingnya sangat enak.
-Benar, 'kan?

321
00:18:19,723 --> 00:18:23,143
Tempat ini mengawetkan daging dengan baik.
Makanlah, semuanya.

322
00:18:23,227 --> 00:18:24,395
Ini enak.

323
00:18:29,191 --> 00:18:30,526
Kau suka daging?

324
00:18:31,110 --> 00:18:32,611
Aku makan potongan besar.

325
00:18:35,406 --> 00:18:36,657
Begitu caranya.

326
00:18:38,450 --> 00:18:41,203
Sersan Han tampak berbeda dari biasanya.

327
00:18:41,620 --> 00:18:42,621
Mereka bermusuhan?

328
00:18:42,705 --> 00:18:43,747
-Dia berbeda?
-Ya.

329
00:18:43,831 --> 00:18:45,833
Ini pasti yang disebut intuisi wanita.

330
00:18:46,417 --> 00:18:47,960
<i>Ada sesuatu di antara mereka?</i>

331
00:18:48,043 --> 00:18:49,420
<i>Apa itu? Bisa beri tahu?</i>

332
00:18:49,837 --> 00:18:51,130
<i>Mereka saling benci.</i>

333
00:18:58,178 --> 00:18:59,930
Indah di malam hari, bukan?

334
00:19:02,850 --> 00:19:04,393
Berhenti mencoba berbasa-basi.

335
00:19:05,477 --> 00:19:06,520
Kenapa kau di sini?

336
00:19:07,187 --> 00:19:10,608
Kau meninggalkan kesatuan.
Kenapa masih ada di sekitar sini?

337
00:19:12,776 --> 00:19:14,528
Bisa-bisanya menyelamatkan orang

338
00:19:15,321 --> 00:19:17,823
saat kau bahkan tak bisa
menyelamatkan rekanmu?

339
00:19:20,826 --> 00:19:21,994
Kenapa?

340
00:19:22,745 --> 00:19:24,830
Kau mau mengurangi rasa bersalahmu?

341
00:19:25,414 --> 00:19:26,624
Apa begitu?

342
00:19:28,250 --> 00:19:29,376
Kau benar.

343
00:19:31,629 --> 00:19:32,963
Apa itu sangat salah?

344
00:19:35,174 --> 00:19:36,759
Apa? Coba katakan sekali lagi.

345
00:19:40,054 --> 00:19:41,388
Biar aku bertanya juga.

346
00:19:41,472 --> 00:19:43,307
-Jawab aku! Sialan!
-Beri tahu aku.

347
00:19:43,766 --> 00:19:47,561
Kau mau aku merasa bersalah selamanya
karena membiarkan saudaramu meninggal?

348
00:19:48,937 --> 00:19:50,147
Kenapa?

349
00:19:50,272 --> 00:19:51,482
Kau menyangkalnya?

350
00:19:53,609 --> 00:19:55,944
Maka beri tahu aku
semua kejadian hari itu.

351
00:20:03,869 --> 00:20:05,496
Dasar kau pengecut.

352
00:20:13,003 --> 00:20:14,713
-Ini enak, bukan?
-Ya.

353
00:20:15,339 --> 00:20:16,423
Wah, panas.

354
00:20:17,466 --> 00:20:18,592
Perlahan.

355
00:20:18,676 --> 00:20:20,511
Makan banyak sayur dengan daging.

356
00:20:20,594 --> 00:20:22,388
Katamu makan lebih banyak daging.

357
00:20:22,971 --> 00:20:24,181
Lebih banyak sayur.

358
00:20:24,807 --> 00:20:26,183
Di mana Sersan Han?

359
00:20:49,373 --> 00:20:50,916
Kenapa dia cepat sekali?

360
00:20:51,667 --> 00:20:53,377
Ke mana dia pergi?

361
00:20:58,257 --> 00:20:59,258
Sersan…

362
00:21:41,008 --> 00:21:44,011
{\an8}HAN WONJIN

363
00:21:44,094 --> 00:21:45,095
Pukul itu!

364
00:21:53,437 --> 00:21:55,981
Aku hanya pakai satu tangan.
Jangan terlalu keras.

365
00:21:56,648 --> 00:21:57,775
Mereka begitu lagi.

366
00:21:59,401 --> 00:22:01,069
Kau tak mengalahkanku.

367
00:22:01,195 --> 00:22:02,821
Ayolah, perlahan.

368
00:22:02,946 --> 00:22:05,199
-Katanya kau tak mengalahkannya.
-Berhenti.

369
00:22:05,282 --> 00:22:06,283
Itu cukup.

370
00:22:08,243 --> 00:22:09,411
Kau tak mengalahkanku.

371
00:22:09,495 --> 00:22:12,039
-Wajahmu hampir meledak tadi.
-Hentikan.

372
00:22:12,122 --> 00:22:13,916
Aku punya kabar. Ayo minum.

373
00:22:14,041 --> 00:22:15,334
-Kau traktir?
-Ya.

374
00:22:15,459 --> 00:22:17,252
-Baiklah.
-Kau tak mengalahkanku.

375
00:22:17,419 --> 00:22:19,776
Baiklah. Astaga, kau sangat gigih.

376
00:22:20,506 --> 00:22:21,673
-Kerja bagus.
-Ya.

377
00:22:21,757 --> 00:22:22,758
-Eunsook.
-Hei.

378
00:22:22,841 --> 00:22:23,847
Halo.

379
00:22:23,926 --> 00:22:24,940
Duduklah.

380
00:22:25,215 --> 00:22:26,925
-Duduk.
-Ambil gelasku.

381
00:22:27,221 --> 00:22:29,223
Ini gelasmu. Bersulang.

382
00:22:30,682 --> 00:22:32,226
-Ada yang mau kukatakan.
-Apa?

383
00:22:35,771 --> 00:22:38,440
Kami akan menikah.

384
00:22:40,567 --> 00:22:41,944
Berhenti bercanda.

385
00:22:42,027 --> 00:22:43,237
-Kau bercanda.
-Gila.

386
00:22:43,320 --> 00:22:45,405
-Itu tak lucu.
-Aku tak bercanda.

387
00:22:45,531 --> 00:22:47,741
Kami akan melaksanakan
pernikahan secepatnya.

388
00:22:48,575 --> 00:22:50,077
Apa maksudmu?

389
00:22:50,202 --> 00:22:54,122
Seperti katanya. Aku akan membuat
dia menjadi pria jujur.

390
00:22:58,252 --> 00:23:00,587
-Dia…
-Apa? kau bilang, "Pria jujur"?

391
00:23:01,046 --> 00:23:03,507
-Kau tak bisa.
-Kenapa tidak?

392
00:23:04,007 --> 00:23:05,300
Chul.

393
00:23:05,384 --> 00:23:08,011
Aku akan membuat adikmu bahagia.

394
00:23:08,095 --> 00:23:09,555
Kenapa melakukan itu?

395
00:23:11,014 --> 00:23:12,599
Ayolah, mereka saling cinta.

396
00:23:12,724 --> 00:23:14,852
Kenapa kau mau buat adikku bahagia?

397
00:23:15,769 --> 00:23:16,854
Benar, 'kan?

398
00:23:17,354 --> 00:23:19,231
Aku paham perasaan Chul.

399
00:23:19,314 --> 00:23:20,941
Apa yang kau bicarakan?

400
00:23:21,066 --> 00:23:23,402
Wonjin pria baik.

401
00:23:23,485 --> 00:23:25,571
Dia tampan dan kepribadiannya baik.

402
00:23:25,654 --> 00:23:27,781
Dia sempurna. Aku setujui pernikahan ini.

403
00:23:28,407 --> 00:23:29,575
Kau bagaimana, Dujin?

404
00:23:29,950 --> 00:23:31,785
Aku agak terkejut sekarang.

405
00:23:32,411 --> 00:23:34,329
-Ayo minum saja.
-Ini gila.

406
00:23:34,413 --> 00:23:36,832
Kenapa air?
Bukankah kau mahir minum alkohol?

407
00:23:37,416 --> 00:23:38,959
Apa kau hamil?

408
00:23:46,425 --> 00:23:47,551
Maaf, Chul.

409
00:23:49,136 --> 00:23:50,846
Kenapa kau minta maaf padanya?

410
00:23:50,971 --> 00:23:53,765
Aku senang mempersiapkan
makanan bergizi ini.

411
00:23:53,974 --> 00:23:56,018
Ini panas. Makan yang banyak.

412
00:23:56,101 --> 00:23:57,311
Terima kasih, Hyosun.

413
00:23:57,603 --> 00:24:00,063
-Ini hari yang baik. Kau harus…
-Kau tersenyum?

414
00:24:00,939 --> 00:24:01,940
Bersulang.

415
00:24:03,317 --> 00:24:05,235
-Aku tak percaya ini.
-Bersulang.

416
00:24:06,653 --> 00:24:08,864
Satu, dua, tiga.

417
00:24:10,198 --> 00:24:12,951
{\an8}HAN WONJIN

418
00:24:27,299 --> 00:24:29,551
Berhenti sembunyi dan keluar.

419
00:24:32,763 --> 00:24:33,847
Keluarlah.

420
00:24:44,975 --> 00:24:46,081
Karena kau di sini,

421
00:24:47,277 --> 00:24:48,320
sapalah saudaraku.

422
00:24:58,121 --> 00:24:59,122
Kau pergi ke gereja?

423
00:25:03,001 --> 00:25:04,962
Halo, aku calon saudara iparmu.

424
00:25:05,045 --> 00:25:06,380
Hentikan itu.

425
00:25:07,005 --> 00:25:10,467
Pasti sulit memiliki saudara
yang tak tahu apa-apa.

426
00:25:10,550 --> 00:25:11,551
Hei, Aneh.

427
00:25:11,635 --> 00:25:14,137
Lihat? Dia bahkan belum menawariku
untuk duduk.

428
00:25:15,222 --> 00:25:17,724
Astaga, kakiku sakit.

429
00:25:19,351 --> 00:25:20,352
Duduk di sini.

430
00:25:21,603 --> 00:25:23,647
-Sungguh?
-Duduklah.

431
00:25:23,939 --> 00:25:24,982
Ya, Pak.

432
00:25:28,402 --> 00:25:30,821
-Aku mau pergi, Wonjin. Ayo.
-Mau pergi?

433
00:25:30,904 --> 00:25:31,947
Ya.

434
00:25:34,449 --> 00:25:35,575
Tunggu aku.

435
00:25:39,329 --> 00:25:42,666
Kulihat keponakanmu sangat lucu.

436
00:25:43,667 --> 00:25:45,335
Namanya Han Jun.

437
00:25:45,711 --> 00:25:46,795
Jun.

438
00:25:47,379 --> 00:25:49,756
Aku ingin bertemu dengannya.
Bisa ajak aku?

439
00:25:49,881 --> 00:25:51,258
Kapan kau menemuinya?

440
00:25:51,383 --> 00:25:52,509
Kenapa harus ajak kau?

441
00:25:53,719 --> 00:25:56,346
-Kau sering mengunjunginya?
-Ya.

442
00:25:59,641 --> 00:26:00,642
Sungguh?

443
00:26:01,101 --> 00:26:02,436
Seberapa tinggi dia?

444
00:26:04,021 --> 00:26:05,522
Ayolah. Beri tahu aku.

445
00:26:06,148 --> 00:26:07,274
Jun…

446
00:26:09,359 --> 00:26:10,485
setinggi ini?

447
00:26:14,698 --> 00:26:16,616
Aku belum pernah menemuinya,

448
00:26:16,700 --> 00:26:19,953
jadi, aku tak tahu kau berbohong
atau tidak.

449
00:26:21,246 --> 00:26:25,292
Jadi, ajak aku
saat kau menemuinya nanti, oke?

450
00:26:26,460 --> 00:26:27,461
Berjanjilah padaku.

451
00:26:29,838 --> 00:26:31,548
Kau lancang padaku?

452
00:26:32,716 --> 00:26:33,967
Kapan aku melakukan itu?

453
00:26:34,551 --> 00:26:36,887
-Aku tak begitu.
-"Aku tak begitu"?

454
00:26:37,012 --> 00:26:38,513
Kau gila. Dasar aneh!

455
00:26:39,681 --> 00:26:41,266
-Kemarilah.
-Tidak, tunggu!

456
00:26:41,349 --> 00:26:42,392
Hei!

457
00:26:42,726 --> 00:26:43,727
Hei!

458
00:26:44,978 --> 00:26:45,979
Wah.

459
00:26:46,104 --> 00:26:47,105
Aku tidak…

460
00:26:47,606 --> 00:26:48,690
Kau cukup cepat.

461
00:26:49,649 --> 00:26:50,734
Tunggu aku.

462
00:26:50,817 --> 00:26:51,902
Ayo.

463
00:27:05,665 --> 00:27:08,418
Harapan terakhir kita
adalah obat baru ini.

464
00:27:08,502 --> 00:27:11,338
Tapi tak ditanggung oleh asuransi,

465
00:27:11,421 --> 00:27:13,173
jadi, biayanya cukup mahal.

466
00:27:33,777 --> 00:27:35,153
Paman Chul.

467
00:27:35,779 --> 00:27:40,492
Kenapa kau menemuiku hanya saat aku tidur?

468
00:27:41,201 --> 00:27:43,870
Maaf, lain kali aku akan
datang siang hari.

469
00:27:44,746 --> 00:27:45,997
Tidurlah lagi.

470
00:27:47,624 --> 00:27:48,792
Maafkan aku.

471
00:28:31,376 --> 00:28:32,377
Chul.

472
00:28:36,840 --> 00:28:39,217
-Ambil ini.
-Kau simpan saja.

473
00:28:39,885 --> 00:28:41,052
Aku tak memerlukannya.

474
00:28:42,262 --> 00:28:44,264
Kau tak melakukan hal ilegal, 'kan?

475
00:28:44,931 --> 00:28:46,016
Tidak.

476
00:28:47,100 --> 00:28:49,603
Kau yakin? Aku cemas.

477
00:28:49,769 --> 00:28:50,896
Aku cemas

478
00:28:51,521 --> 00:28:53,148
kau bisa berakhir seperti dia.

479
00:28:54,816 --> 00:28:58,278
Jangan mencemaskan itu. Jaga saja dirimu.

480
00:28:59,154 --> 00:29:01,114
Seorang ibu harus kuat demi anaknya.

481
00:29:02,365 --> 00:29:03,825
Fokuslah merawat Jun.

482
00:29:05,827 --> 00:29:06,828
Sampai jumpa.

483
00:29:12,834 --> 00:29:15,503
<i>Divisi Bisnis Sungai Han telah mengeruk</i>

484
00:29:15,587 --> 00:29:17,839
{\an8}<i>dasar sungai dua bulan terakhir</i>

485
00:29:18,215 --> 00:29:21,843
<i>untuk menambah kapal pesiar lebih besar</i>
<i>ke barisan sebelumnya.</i>

486
00:29:22,135 --> 00:29:23,595
<i>Tapi saat </i>River Ferry

487
00:29:23,678 --> 00:29:26,514
<i>melewati persimpangan Sungai Han</i>
<i>dan Anyangchecon,</i>

488
00:29:26,598 --> 00:29:29,851
<i>bagian bawah haluannya tersangkut</i>
<i>di gumuk pasir sungai.</i>

489
00:29:29,976 --> 00:29:32,771
