491
00:29:34,814 --> 00:29:36,191
{\an8}<i>demi terpilihnya wali kota Seoul.</i>

492
00:29:36,274 --> 00:29:37,400
{\an8}PARK DONGSIK
KEPALA DESA NELAYAN

493
00:29:37,484 --> 00:29:38,944
{\an8}<i>Siapa tahu apa hubungannya</i>

494
00:29:39,027 --> 00:29:40,779
{\an8}<i>dengan perusahaan kapal pesiar itu?</i>

495
00:29:41,613 --> 00:29:42,822
<i>Lihat apa yang terjadi.</i>

496
00:29:42,906 --> 00:29:44,616
<i>Jika dia ikuti prosedur benar…</i>

497
00:29:54,376 --> 00:29:55,585
Masalahnya cukup serius,

498
00:29:55,710 --> 00:29:57,212
kau harus tetap di kantor.

499
00:29:57,921 --> 00:29:59,965
Melakukan apa? Makan sampah ini?

500
00:30:00,548 --> 00:30:03,551
-Anggap saja kampanye.
-Singkirkan ini dari hadapanku!

501
00:30:05,262 --> 00:30:07,097
Ini membuatku tak nafsu makan.

502
00:30:07,514 --> 00:30:09,224
Mau kubawakan kotak makan siang?

503
00:30:09,349 --> 00:30:10,809
Dengan dua pil pencernaanku.

504
00:30:11,268 --> 00:30:12,269
Baik, Pak.

505
00:30:16,856 --> 00:30:18,275
Pemimpin Hwang menelepon?

506
00:30:24,906 --> 00:30:25,907
Ini ketiga kalinya.

507
00:30:25,991 --> 00:30:26,996
PEMIMPIN HWANG MANDAE

508
00:30:27,071 --> 00:30:28,410
Kau mau menjawabnya?

509
00:30:30,954 --> 00:30:33,999
<i>Mereka seharusnya sadar</i>
<i>dengan waktu pasang,</i>

510
00:30:34,082 --> 00:30:36,084
<i>tapi kabarnya, mereka lama berhenti,</i>

511
00:30:36,167 --> 00:30:38,962
<i>sehingga melewatkan waktu</i>
<i>saat air berada paling tinggi.</i>

512
00:30:40,130 --> 00:30:41,131
WALI KOTA SEOUL

513
00:30:41,214 --> 00:30:42,882
<i>Mereka mau selamatkan </i>River Ferry,

514
00:30:42,966 --> 00:30:45,010
<i>yang terjebak selama percobaan.</i>

515
00:30:45,343 --> 00:30:48,138
<i>Tapi karena rendahnya</i>
<i>level air Sungai Han…</i>

516
00:30:53,601 --> 00:30:55,770
Orang-orang sialan itu.

517
00:30:57,230 --> 00:30:59,858
Mereka datang seperti anjing
saat kuberi makanan.

518
00:30:59,941 --> 00:31:01,109
Astaga.

519
00:31:14,873 --> 00:31:15,957
Direktur Go.

520
00:31:18,335 --> 00:31:20,295
-Ya, Pak.
-Keponakanku.

521
00:31:20,920 --> 00:31:21,921
Ya, Paman.

522
00:31:23,089 --> 00:31:24,174
Ya, Pak Pemimpin.

523
00:31:26,426 --> 00:31:29,512
Kau pikir aku menjadikanmu direktur…

524
00:31:30,638 --> 00:31:31,973
untuk menyalakan rokokku?

525
00:31:32,098 --> 00:31:33,099
Tidak, Pak.

526
00:31:33,183 --> 00:31:35,894
Bisa kau beri tahu
kenapa aku masih harus mengurus

527
00:31:35,977 --> 00:31:37,145
semua masalah itu?

528
00:31:37,729 --> 00:31:38,730
Maafkan aku, Pak.

529
00:31:49,949 --> 00:31:52,202
Kau tahu
betapa pentingnya proyek ini, 'kan?

530
00:31:52,577 --> 00:31:54,287
-Aku tahu, Pak.
-Aku akan…

531
00:31:55,121 --> 00:31:57,999
mengevaluasi sepenuhnya apa kau layak

532
00:31:58,833 --> 00:32:00,168
berada di posisimu ini.

533
00:32:01,169 --> 00:32:02,754
Aku akan urus itu, Pak.

534
00:32:07,217 --> 00:32:08,802
Pak, ponselmu…

535
00:32:11,221 --> 00:32:13,836
Katakan. Aku harus gunakan
Dokter atau Pemukul?

536
00:32:14,766 --> 00:32:15,934
Dokter bertindak rapi.

537
00:32:16,017 --> 00:32:17,841
Pemukul akan sakit dan kacau.

538
00:32:18,895 --> 00:32:19,979
Sekarang,…

539
00:32:21,189 --> 00:32:22,399
aku tak mau yang rapi.

540
00:32:29,697 --> 00:32:30,865
Berapa kali, Pak?

541
00:32:31,116 --> 00:32:34,619
Kau tak dengar dia? Pukul dia
sampai babak kesembilan.

542
00:32:35,870 --> 00:32:36,871
Baik, Pak.

543
00:32:53,471 --> 00:32:57,725
PELAYARAN SUNGAI KYUNGIN

544
00:33:04,983 --> 00:33:06,401
Lihat dia.

545
00:33:12,490 --> 00:33:19,456
{\an8}SELAMAT ATAS PELAYARANNYA

546
