617
00:37:29,997 --> 00:37:31,124
Ya, memang.

618
00:37:55,398 --> 00:37:56,899
Sialan.

619
00:37:57,567 --> 00:37:59,986
Ini sepatu buatan tangan. Sial.

620
00:38:03,698 --> 00:38:05,908
Apa ini? Aku tak tahu ada tempat ini.

621
00:38:07,118 --> 00:38:08,202
Ini indah.

622
00:38:09,454 --> 00:38:11,414
Akan kuminta Paman bangun kantor di sini.

623
00:38:28,014 --> 00:38:29,432
Ada yang bisa kubantu?

624
00:38:29,807 --> 00:38:31,350
Apa Baek Chul di sini?

625
00:38:33,186 --> 00:38:34,353
Hei, Baek Chul!

626
