677
00:42:06,357 --> 00:42:09,068
-Kau mau coba?
-Tidak, lupakan saja.

678
00:42:11,529 --> 00:42:13,364
Ini panas.

679
00:42:18,619 --> 00:42:19,954
Hei, lebih dekat!

680
00:42:21,747 --> 00:42:24,959
Lebih dekat! Ke arah sini!

681
00:42:26,293 --> 00:42:27,837
Sedikit lebih dekat!

682
00:42:29,964 --> 00:42:31,257
Baiklah, berhenti!

683
00:43:11,130 --> 00:43:12,131
Ikuti aku.

684
00:43:17,553 --> 00:43:18,554
{\an8}LEMARI PENDINGIN

685
00:43:27,938 --> 00:43:28,939
Ini dia.

686
00:43:34,403 --> 00:43:35,529
Sial.

687
00:43:35,613 --> 00:43:36,614
Hei.

688
00:43:37,114 --> 00:43:39,408
Hati-hatilah. Cepat angkat ini.

689
00:43:43,913 --> 00:43:46,290
<i>Sial, hujannya deras.</i>

690
00:43:46,749 --> 00:43:48,667
<i>Hei, Dokter. Kau sudah mulai?</i>

691
00:43:48,751 --> 00:43:49,752
Ya, Pak.

692
00:43:50,999 --> 00:43:52,296
Kita akan mulai.

693
00:43:52,379 --> 00:43:55,174
<i>Aku akan desak orang-orang itu</i>
<i>untuk segera selesaikan,</i>

694
00:43:55,299 --> 00:43:56,425
