695
00:43:56,801 --> 00:43:57,802
Oke.

696
00:43:59,804 --> 00:44:00,846
Berapa lama lagi?

697
00:44:01,180 --> 00:44:03,390
Ini sangat berkarat, jadi,…

698
00:44:03,516 --> 00:44:04,809
Bukan itu pertanyaanku.

699
00:44:05,184 --> 00:44:06,435
Akan kuselesaikan segera.

